name: Tracked ... Delushiz Game Jam Edition
description:
I made this in Processing during a 48 hour gamejam.

Its very unfinished ... but eh ... Brandon said we had to upload our stuff to itch.io ... so ... tell him it was a bad idea for me

Regardless ...

Its a platformer ... use arrows to move ... press F to push robots ... you have a fatigue meter that is always going down ... during night press down-arrow to fill it up ...

 if it runs out ... you die ... 

if you run out of health .. you die ...

you cant win this game ...

on a side note ... press * to get to the level editor
